828
00:43:58,480 --> 00:44:01,240
Eighth Prince, please sit.

829
00:44:17,900 --> 00:44:24,740
The Goddess of Mercy sits in the hall.

830
00:44:24,740 --> 00:44:33,240
The golden boy and girl stand by her sides.

831
00:44:34,740 --> 00:44:41,760
Both of them obviously look like husband and wife.

832
00:44:41,760 --> 00:44:50,560
Who shall light the incense burner?

833
00:44:51,720 --> 00:44:59,000
Deity of Marriage may control the marriage of everyone,

834
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:06,600
but only those who are in love can be matched together.

835
00:45:06,600 --> 00:45:13,800
Those clay figures and wooden carvings are just figurines.

836
00:45:13,800 --> 00:45:23,640
They don't understand human courtship.

837
00:45:23,640 --> 00:45:29,600
Brother Liang.

838
00:45:30,740 --> 00:45:38,360
Both of them have feelings for each other,

839
00:45:38,360 --> 00:45:45,520
