840
00:45:45,520 --> 00:45:52,840
Let Goddess of Mercy be the matchmaker.

841
00:45:52,840 --> 00:46:04,180
Come, let's have a wedding on their behalf.

842
00:46:04,180 --> 00:46:08,720
